{"tid":252642,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實痴身點樣拿挰？","createTime":"2017-05-21T18:39:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T19:57:37.000Z","uid":74823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c63d65c23b74947287d28d6e52ea5da5136deb04","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:39:25.000Z","msg":"啱啱睇到 唔知點做好女朋友個POST<br />\n<br />\n啲人話樓豬痴身 將個中心擺曬係條仔到已經係死症<br />\n<br />\n咁點樣拿挰痴身啊其實？<br />\n<br />\n痴身如果一星期見3-4日 未必由晏就到夜晚咁長時間啦 咁叫唔叫痴身？<br />\n<br />\n同埋點樣拿挰有朋友同埋重色輕友呢？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得呢方面平衡做得幾差下<br />\n<br />\n因為我覺得同另一半出街玩就最開心 最多野講 就變到唔想搵自己原本啲朋友<br />\n<br />\nSEM BREAK一個月可能見3-5次朋友 咁叫唔叫太少呢？<br />\n<br />\n我其實又無好多真心朋友 都係得4 5個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時唔係想痴身<br />\n<br />\n返份補習 又係返3日 2.5小時一次<br />\n<br />\n但另一半頭先話：我緊係會陪妳啦 但我唔得閒 妳都可以搵朋友架嘛<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪解讀為 佢覺得我好痴身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c16c98d7ec61fe6770ae1c5bfb7c8ed029760280","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:40:00.000Z","msg":"凌晨有無秒回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c6d52afebe2c161618312d002fe81822347ca93","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"255405e678356eebff57c1ca3efcaf9d7a8c10a6","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:43:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"16d4c97499f3306a33b3cb57930ff81ec093ccdd","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:43:47.000Z","msg":"一推再推"},{"pid":"a31e5e05f4df68e5a80b7bd1569a1febb9bfdd59","tid":252642,"uid":13538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:47:09.000Z","msg":"其實我認為冇一個定義<br />\n兩個人一齊舒服咪得囉<br />\n唔需求執著係&quot;痴唔痴身&quot;度"},{"pid":"cfff29dd915f6c57874483e708643fcc5ace7e27","tid":252642,"uid":74823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T18:58:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實我認為冇一個定義<br />\n兩個人一齊舒服咪得囉<br />\n唔需求執著係&quot;痴唔痴身&quot;度</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等到天荒地老先有人覆我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但普遍人都好似唔喜歡痴身女朋友"},{"pid":"5dcc02407e3c5c6e953ee14c01d167614931c416","tid":252642,"uid":73509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:01:00.000Z","msg":"鍾意你就唔癡身，唔鍾意你就好撚癡身"},{"pid":"64bb2b0e63d5315aab820486f261fa7decb2f0f1","tid":252642,"uid":101804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:57:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鍾意你就唔癡身，唔鍾意你就好撚癡身</blockquote><br />\n同意 鍾意咪岩岩好啊 唔煩唔討厭<br />\n淡左或者唔鍾意你 才是死症"}]}